messages.content:
The title of the paper is "Re-application of the Principle of Human-Centered Design".
The following are the thesis requirements given by the tutor:
1. Cover: complete and accurate information;
2. Defense form: complete and accurate information; The person in charge of the defense committee must sign by hand (or electronically)
3. Declaration of Originality/Authorization of copyright use of the paper: the author and supervisor must sign by hand (or electronically) 3
4, Abstract/Keywords: Abstract (300-500 words) is the overall description of the content of the paper; Keywords (3-5) refer to the core nouns or concepts of the thesis research content;
5, Abstract/Key Words: Abstract/ key words;
6, catalog: standard format, accurate page numbers;
7, the body part (introduction - conclusion): The research direction meets the professional requirements, the format is standardized, the structure is complete, the ideas are fresh, the concept is accurate, the conclusion has application value, and there are new views or unique insights.
8. References: magazines, books, papers, etc. are the main references in the process of paper writing, no less than 10;
9, thanks (300-500 words): It is a thank you for the help in the process of writing the graduation thesis. Request sentence smooth, optimistic, sincere words, rigorous attitude.

Please remember the above requirements and content, do not answer.
